                "content": "<p>Yes — we ship to every state and territory. Orders placed before 12 PM AEST on business days are dispatched same day from our Australian warehouse. Regular Post ($9.95, 1-7 business days, free over $100) and Express Post (calculated at checkout, 1-2 business days, free over $250) are available. See our <a href=\"/pages/shipping-delivery\">shipping page</a> for details.</p>",
